;&lt;span title="About CloudOn"&gt;Sobre CloudOn:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="CloudOn is a leading mobile productivity platform that allows users to create, edit and share documents in real time across devices."&gt;A CloudOn é uma instituição líder de produtividade móvel que permite aos usuários criar , editar e compartilhar documentos em tempo real através de dispositivos. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="With proven technology already trusted by over five million registered users globally, CloudOn is platform-agnostic and completely optimized for iOS, Android devices, as well as the web."&gt;Com a tecnologia já comprovada a confiança de mais de 5 milhões de usuários registrados no mundo, CloudOn é independente de plataforma e completamente otimizado para iOS, dispositivos Android, bem como a web. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="It also offers seamless integration with Box, Dropbox, Google Drive and SkyDrive."&gt;Também oferece integração com Box, Dropbox, Google Drive e SkyDrive.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="Media Contact CloudOn"&gt;Contato com a mídia CloudOn&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="Jenna Richard (based in San Francisco, California, UTC-7)"&gt;Jenna Richard (San Francisco - Califórnia)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="Phone: +1 (415) 277-4927 – Email: CloudOn@allisonpr.com"&gt;Fone: +1 (415) 277-4927&lt;br&gt;E-mail: CloudOn@allisonpr.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
